user<br />\n應該用呢用去都係基本cmd ，用到2成function 度<br />\n連page up down 都唔記得<br />\n覺得最好用 :%s/ / /g</blockquote><br />\n你search 有無轉regex flavour <br />\n好唔慣() 要打\\(\\) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n通常都係普通text search,係做 sed n replace 先會用regex。vim用慣真係返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5141681350abb9795bb7c761efaf9688e3a78a","tid":294902,"uid":105553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T18:05:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Vi 同vim有冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nvi 係 UC Berkeley嘅BSD到黎，vim係後人寫嘅另一個兼容版本，vim功能俾vi多好多。不過我vim都係當vi用，無咩用vim嘅新增功能。"}]}